{"tid":1685609,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗暴之戰】內地人憂反中情緒升溫 「不想在撕裂的城市建立家庭」","createTime":"2019-10-31T15:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T15:56:16.000Z","uid":283725,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3430f7a839f7a8330beec8f89e26a655775cd1f1","tid":1685609,"uid":283725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:41:06.000Z","msg":"似乎抗爭真係有啲成績<br />\n<br />\n一名30多歲姓陳的女投資銀行家目前在本港一間中國私募基金工作，她住在香港接近10年，但現在已向上司要求可否搬到北京。「住在一個你感到本地人不太歡迎你的城市，實在感到非常沮喪。動亂看不到盡頭&hellip;&hellip;我肯定不想在這個破爛、撕裂的城市建立家庭及養兒育女。」<br />\n<br />\n一位姓李的律師行中國合夥人亦在香港生活了十多年，他透露自己的親身經歷，聲稱與兩個兒子到銅鑼灣一個商場購物時，當他的兒子以普通話告知一名售貨員想買玩具時，對方竟然向兩個孩子大喊，令他們受驚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191031/60212170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191031%2F60212170&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eL%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=fa207b4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191031%2F60212170&h=0a09ddea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191031/60212170</a>"},{"pid":"cfb4ea83ae6966d2ebbca7f30f507b5d725badfc","tid":1685609,"uid":205937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"啱啦啱啦 以後咪撚落嚟就最好"},{"pid":"f44336cbd56b0ff040bd8d7efddc83f2af0d5ff5","tid":1685609,"uid":303862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"返去<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">祖国</span>既懷抱"},{"pid":"f89b97a657b0e6c3c66014389f5d1037dae8ffb1","tid":1685609,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:56:16.000Z","msg":"香港啲野唔賣比支那人喎 你可以點"}]}